                                    </svg>
                                    <span>Presentación de informe de investigación</span>
                                </div>
                                <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium border border-gray-300 bg-white text-gray-700">15 Mayo 2025</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between p-2 border rounded-md bg-slate-50">
                                <div class="flex items-center">
                                    <svg class="mr-2 h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
